videos.headline: Merritt dives for game-winning Arkansas State TD
videos.description: Layne Hatcher finds Kirk Merritt diving into the end zone with less than a minute left in the fourth quarter, giving Arkansas State a 28-27 win over Coastal Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Merritt dives for game-winning Arkansas State TD) 2019/11/16 ESHEET
